ZH: 请你呼叫一辆出租车。
EN: Please call a taxi.

ZH: 如果有任何问题，请呼叫客服部门。
EN: If you have any questions, please call the customer service department.

ZH: 我可以借用你的手机呼叫一下吗？
EN: Can I borrow your phone to make a call?

ZH: 情况紧急，赶紧呼叫救护车！
EN: The situation is urgent, call an ambulance quickly!

ZH: 我刚刚呼叫了警察，他们会很快赶到。
EN: I just called the police, they will arrive soon.

ZH: 在这个单位，我们只能使用内线呼叫。
EN: In this office, we can only make internal calls.

ZH: 请不要在这里呼叫，这是禁止通话的区域。
EN: Please do not make calls here, it is a restricted area.

ZH: 可以使用手机呼叫国际长途吗？
EN: Can I use my cell phone to make international calls?

ZH: 我需要呼叫一个专家来解决这个问题。
EN: I need to call in an expert to solve this problem.

ZH: 她刚才呼叫了我，说她会迟到。
EN: She just called me to say she will be late.

ZH: 呼叫警察是你唯一的选择。
EN: Calling the police is your only option.

ZH: 我刚刚呼叫了客户，他们很满意我们的服务。
EN: I just called the client, they are satisfied with our service.

ZH: 请你呼叫一个员工开会室。
EN: Please call an employee to the conference room.

ZH: 呼叫医生！这个人需要紧急治疗！
EN: Call a doctor! This person needs urgent treatment!

ZH: 我用手机呼叫了妈妈，告诉她我要晚归。
EN: I called my mom using my cellphone to let her know I will be home late.

ZH: 请为我呼叫一辆豪华轿车。
EN: Please call a luxury sedan for me.

ZH: 他用大声呼叫来引起我的注意。
EN: He called out loudly to get my attention.

ZH: 这个应用可以免费呼叫国际电话。
EN: This app allows you to make free international calls.

ZH: 呼叫接线员，我需要帮助。
EN: Call the operator, I need assistance.

ZH: 我们需要呼叫消防队员来熄灭大火。
EN: We need to call the firefighters to put out the fire.
